item.dc:creator: @bigh51 bigh51
item.description:

[quote=“Alecks, post:16, topic:235397”][quote author=bigh51 link=topic=310447.msg2478558#msg2478558 date=1223409456]

[quote author=Alecks link=topic=310447.msg2478499#msg2478499 date=1223407799]

Could you possibly upload the other files?

Sorry the person who sent me this only sent me the barebone. I don’t even think he has the other files.

VarekD isn’t the Stork PK source. It’s the new framework Stork was working on, but never completed.
[/quote]Why would he say “aka stork pk source” if it’s not the source and it’s just a framework?

Because its the source that Stork was selling. Its a better version of the original. I mean think about it, if he was writing a new one, wouldn’t it be more stable/better than the old one? And its not like I’m trying to have to so you can DL it and run it right off the bat. It’s just code to help out some people, instead of some stupid noob who bought it from Hixk saying “new storkpk server”.
[/quote]I personally would prefer having the one before it got shut down, with the cp and sql files and conf files and everything exactly the same.

Yeah but the majority of the old stork pk source is in this source too. Just re-written.[/quote]Yeah, but not all of it. This doesn’t have a points system afaik.
